          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Class rooms here are equipped with projectors and screens which are helpful for the students",
          "name": "Robinson A",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The infrastructure is good but the some of the facilities over here are not that good compared to other colleges",
          "name": "Robinson A",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Yes really good college in Bangalore. teachers good to touch",
