          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "And there are regular events and activities conducted in the college",
          "name": "Tharun",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Best thing about the college is that we have a great infrastructure.",
