        },
        {
          "text": "the thing i like from my college is there staffs any the way they teach to the students are so good and the campus is so good out there i way teachers approach to students are way good this is what i like from my college.",
          "name": "Divya s",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "I dislike about my college is management",
