          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "No ground for students who wish to play sports",
          "name": "Robinson A",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Labs here are not good systems are very outdated with worst update and very slow",
